posting_body: ['VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'Artizan, managed by Sares-Regis Group', '219 9th Ave', 'Oakland, CA 94606', 'show contact info', "It's Oakland living-but better.", 'In Brooklyn Basin, coastline meets skyline, and Artizan is your chance to live right on the waterfront.', 'Lease now at Artizan!', 'Say yes to Artizan living.', 'Only in Oakland.', 'Artizan is your chance to live right on the waterfront.', 'Our brand-new, master-planned neighborhood welcomes a mix of everything you want from your local community: parks and trails, Bay area access, food from all around the world, boating, bars, and more.', 'Choose your one or two bedroom apartment today, and get ready to wake up on the waterfront.', 'Our community offers access to all the spaces you need-coworking, lounges, pet spas, clubrooms and all the luxury amenities in between.', 'And did you hear about our expansive pool deck?', "It's the perfect place to watch golden hour sunsets float over San Francisco Bay.", 'A sun-soaked paradise.', 'Our Resort Style Community Features', '\uf076\tKeyless Entry System', '\uf076\tSpacious Interiors w/ 9ft High Ceilings', '\uf076\tIn Home Washer/Dryer', '\uf076\tPlank- Style Floors', '\uf076\tStainless-Steel Samsung Appliances', '\uf076\tCentral AC/Heat', '\uf076\tBalconies & Private Terrace', '\uf076\tBay View and Waterfront Lifestyle', '\uf076\tComplimentary Bike Storage', '\uf076\tResort -Style Pool & Deck', '\uf076\tEV Parking', '\uf076\tBusiness Center - Co-Working Spaces', '\uf076\tRooftop Lounge w/Water Front Views', '\uf076\tSecure Package Room', '\uf076\tFitness Center', '\uf076\tPet Spa']
